    <content>&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":rocket:"&gt;🚀&lt;/span&gt; Don't Miss Out on ASUG Tech Connect: Know before you go &lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":globe_with_meridians:"&gt;🌐&lt;/span&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":calendar:"&gt;📅&lt;/span&gt; Date: October 19&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":three_o_clock:"&gt;🕒&lt;/span&gt; Time: 1:00 pm Eastern&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":round_pushpin:"&gt;📍&lt;/span&gt; Where: Online - Anywhere You Are!&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":glowing_star:"&gt;🌟&lt;/span&gt; Mark your calendars for the ASUG Tech Connect webcast: Know Before You Go!&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":link:"&gt;🔗&lt;/span&gt; Register now:&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://www.asug.com/events/know-before-you-go-asug-tech-connect" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;https://www.asug.com/events/know-before-you-go-asug-tech-connect&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":globe_with_meridians:"&gt;🌐&lt;/span&gt; Webcast details:&lt;BR /&gt;Here's why you should join us:&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":keycap_1:"&gt;1️⃣&lt;/span&gt; Event Preview: Get a sneak peek into what ASUG Tech Connect has in store for you. Discover the hot topics, speakers, and key takeaways that will help your event journey. &lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":light_bulb:"&gt;💡&lt;/span&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":keycap_2:"&gt;2️⃣&lt;/span&gt; Networking Insights: Learn how to maximize your networking opportunities at the event. Meet tech leaders, experts, and peers who can help you soar to new heights in your career. &lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":handshake:"&gt;🤝&lt;/span&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":keycap_3:"&gt;3️⃣&lt;/span&gt; Tips and Tricks: Get exclusive tips on how to make the most of your ASUG Tech Connect experience. &lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":books:"&gt;📚&lt;/span&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":keycap_4:"&gt;4️⃣&lt;/span&gt; Q&amp;amp;A Session: Have burning questions about the event? Our panel of experts will be there to answer them live during the webcast. &lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":speaking_head:"&gt;🗣&lt;/span&gt;️&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;Let's kickstart your ASUG Tech Connect journey together! Register now and get ready to dive into the world of technology, innovation, and endless possibilities. &lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":rocket:"&gt;🚀&lt;/span&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;A href="https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/?keywords=asugtechconnect&amp;amp;highlightedUpdateUrns=urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7114916857098240001" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;#ASUGTechConnect&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/?keywords=webcast&amp;amp;highlightedUpdateUrns=urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7114916857098240001" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;#Webcast&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/?keywords=techevent&amp;amp;highlightedUpdateUrns=urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7114916857098240001" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;#TechEvent&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/?keywords=networking&amp;amp;highlightedUpdateUrns=urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7114916857098240001" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;#Networking&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/?keywords=innovation&amp;amp;highlightedUpdateUrns=urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7114916857098240001" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;#Innovation&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/?keywords=technology&amp;amp;highlightedUpdateUrns=urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7114916857098240001" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;#Technology&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/?keywords=learnandgrow&amp;amp;highlightedUpdateUrns=urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7114916857098240001" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;#LearnAndGrow&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/?keywords=techcommunity&amp;amp;highlightedUpdateUrns=urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7114916857098240001" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;#TechCommunity&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/?keywords=stayahead&amp;amp;highlightedUpdateUrns=urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7114916857098240001" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;#StayAhead&lt;/A&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;See you at the webcast! &lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":globe_with_meridians:"&gt;🌐&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":sparkles:"&gt;✨&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
