    <title>Call for Papers is officially open for SAP for Utilities, Presented by ASUG - September, 2024</title>
    <updated>2024-01-29T16:27:16.823000+01:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>TammyPowlas</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/82</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":loudspeaker:"&gt;📢&lt;/span&gt;Exciting News! Call for Papers is Now Open! &lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":loudspeaker:"&gt;📢&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Call for Papers is officially open for SAP for Utilities, Presented by ASUG - September, 2024&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Source: ASUG" style="width: 770px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/55078iC6551E0923B258D5/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="sap4u2024.jpg" alt="Source: ASUG" /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-caption" onclick="event.preventDefault();"&gt;Source: ASUG&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":books:"&gt;📚&lt;/span&gt;Conference Themes are as follows:&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;SAP S/4HANA&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;The Business of Utilities&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Enterprise Asset Management ​&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Meter to Cash&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Business Intelligence and Analytics​&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Technology&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Artificial Intelligence&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Roadmaps&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;SAP Support&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":spiral_calendar:"&gt;🗓&lt;/span&gt;️ Event Date: September 9 – 11, 2024, Miami, Florida&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":party_popper:"&gt;🎉&lt;/span&gt;We invite everyone to submit their abstracts for consideration. Share your insights, discoveries, and innovations in Utilities.&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":link:"&gt;🔗&lt;/span&gt;Submit your abstract here:&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;A class="" href="https://lnkd.in/emysya8k" target="_self" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;https://lnkd.in/emysya8k&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/customer-relationship-management-blogs-by-members/call-for-papers-is-officially-open-for-sap-for-utilities-presented-by-asug/ba-p/13585381"/>
