  </entry>
  <entry>
    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-blogs-by-members/join-the-asug-february-6-business-technology-platform-townhall/ba-p/13587338</id>
    <title>Join the ASUG February 6 Business Technology Platform Townhall</title>
    <updated>2024-01-30T15:35:40.539000+01:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>TammyPowlas</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/82</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;The ASUG Business Technology Platform (BTP) Community Alliance Town Hall is a unique event that brings ASUG Research and ASUG Content leadership to share plans for 2024.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="20240206townhall.jpg" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/56296iDFD3A211F4668C0B/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="20240206townhall.jpg" alt="20240206townhall.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Join us as ASUG Director of Research, Marissa Gilbert, and ASUG Director of Content Strategy, Kelly Dowling, guide us through what's in store for the BTP community in 2024.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;This discussion will include:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Overview of the BTP Year-Round Programming Approach.&lt;BR /&gt;Review of ASUG BTP Research&lt;BR /&gt;New BTP Community Alliance Map&lt;BR /&gt;Open Forum Discussion&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Register here:&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://www.asug.com/events/asug-business-technology-platform-btp-community-alliance-town-hall-3" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;https://www.asug.com/events/asug-business-technology-platform-btp-community-alliance-town-hall-3&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;or try the QR Code below:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="qrcode.jpg" style="width: 536px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/56268i80B1683F591FCEC8/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="qrcode.jpg" alt="qrcode.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;It's a great opportunity ask your questions, let ASUG know what you want out of 2024, and learn what other ASUG members have to say about BTP.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-blogs-by-members/join-the-asug-february-6-business-technology-platform-townhall/ba-p/13587338"/>
    <published>2024-01-30T15:35:40.539000+01:00</published>
  </entry>
